---
import WikiLayout from '../layouts/WikiLayout.astro';
import TableOfContents from '../components/TableOfContents.astro';
import InfoBox from '../components/InfoBox.astro';

const pageTitle = "Welcome to Shoppland Wiki";

// These would typically come from a content management system or markdown files
const headings = [
  { depth: 2, slug: "about-shoppland", text: "About Shoppland" },
  { depth: 2, slug: "getting-started", text: "Getting Started" },
  { depth: 2, slug: "how-to-use-this-wiki", text: "How to Use This Wiki" },
  { depth: 2, slug: "key-features", text: "Key Features" },
];
---

<WikiLayout title={pageTitle}>
  <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">{pageTitle}</h1>
    <div class="flex gap-2">
      <a href="#" class="text-sm px-3 py-1 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded-md text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-50 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800">
        View history
      </a>
      <a href="#" class="text-sm px-3 py-1 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-neutral-800 rounded-md text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 hover:bg-neutral-50 dark:hover:bg-neutral-800">
        Discussion
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <TableOfContents headings={headings} />

  <InfoBox type="info" title="Wiki Status">
    This wiki is continuously updated with the latest information about Shoppland. Last updated: May 2025.
  </InfoBox>

  <h2 id="about-shoppland">About Shoppland</h2>
  <p>
    Shoppland is a comprehensive e-commerce platform designed to connect buyers and sellers in a seamless online shopping experience. 
    Launched in 2023, Shoppland has quickly grown to become one of the most user-friendly and feature-rich online marketplaces.
  </p>
  <p>
    With a focus on intuitive design and customer satisfaction, Shoppland offers a wide range of products across multiple categories, 
    from electronics and fashion to home goods and specialty items. The platform provides tools for both shoppers and sellers to 
    engage in secure, efficient transactions.
  </p>

  <h2 id="getting-started">Getting Started</h2>
  <p>
    New to Shoppland? This section will help you understand the basics of using the platform, whether you're looking to shop or sell.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="/introduction/what-is-shoppland">What is Shoppland?</a> - An overview of the platform and its purpose</li>
    <li><a href="/user-guide/creating-an-account">Creating an Account</a> - Step-by-step guide to setting up your Shoppland account</li>
    <li><a href="/user-guide/browsing-products">Browsing Products</a> - How to navigate and find products on Shoppland</li>
    <li><a href="/seller-info/becoming-a-seller">Becoming a Seller</a> - Information for those interested in selling on Shoppland</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="how-to-use-this-wiki">How to Use This Wiki</h2>
  <p>
    This wiki is organized into several main sections, each focusing on different aspects of Shoppland:
  </p>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Getting Started</strong> - Basic information for new users</li>
    <li><strong>User Guide</strong> - Detailed instructions for using Shoppland as a shopper</li>
    <li><strong>Features</strong> - In-depth explanations of Shoppland's capabilities</li>
    <li><strong>Seller Information</strong> - Resources for sellers and vendors</li>
    <li><strong>Technical</strong> - Technical specifications and API documentation</li>
  </ol>
  <p>
    You can navigate through these sections using the sidebar on the left. Each page includes a table of contents 
    to help you find specific information quickly.
  </p>

  <InfoBox type="success" title="Quick Tip">
    Use the search function at the top of the page to quickly find specific topics across the entire wiki.
  </InfoBox>

  <h2 id="key-features">Key Features</h2>
  <p>
    Shoppland offers a variety of features designed to enhance the online shopping experience:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>User-Friendly Interface</strong> - Intuitive design that makes navigation and shopping simple</li>
    <li><strong>Secure Transactions</strong> - Advanced security measures to protect user data and financial information</li>
    <li><strong>Comprehensive Search</strong> - Powerful search functionality to help users find exactly what they're looking for</li>
    <li><strong>Reviews and Ratings</strong> - Community-driven product evaluations to guide purchasing decisions</li>
    <li><strong>Wishlist Feature</strong> - Save items for future reference or purchase</li>
    <li><strong>Seller Dashboard</strong> - Tools for sellers to manage inventory, orders, and analytics</li>
    <li><strong>Mobile Compatibility</strong> - Responsive design and dedicated mobile app for shopping on the go</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Explore the wiki to learn more about these features and how to make the most of your Shoppland experience.
  </p>
</WikiLayout>